ComicInfo.Summary: As the web of lies and deceit begin to unravel, F5 learns their true fate. Penny and the rest of F5 discover that there is more than one party interested in Kessler's new weapon of mass destruction! The last leg of their first mission becomes lethal as the team is betrayed by one of their own, and a team member dies. Penny wants revenge---on the double agent! Find out who the double agent is! Illustrated and written by creator, Tony Daniel, inks by Rich Bonk and Colors by Steve Firchow.
